29
00:01:59,191 --> 00:02:00,986
Bluebirds, dillies, love boats?

30
00:02:01,150 --> 00:02:04,142
I heard Halberstrom might not
even hire anyone this year.

31
00:02:04,311 --> 00:02:05,503
Well, I'm not anyone.

