40
00:02:35,629 --> 00:02:38,346
At the risk of sounding schmaltzy,
I just wanna tell you...

41
00:02:38,506 --> 00:02:41,020
...that you're a schmuck.
I hope I never see you again.

42
00:02:41,226 --> 00:02:44,343
Thanks, Tommy. I know how hard
it was for you to say that.

43
00:02:44,506 --> 00:02:48,784
You're a good doctor, Ben. I just thought
you were gonna practice real medicine.

44
00:02:50,226 --> 00:02:53,184
Think I'm making a mistake
going to Halberstrom?

45
00:02:54,466 --> 00:02:57,616
No. Cosmetic surgery is clean...

46
00:02:57,786 --> 00:03:01,094
...you make tons of money,
nobody dies.

47
00:03:01,506 --> 00:03:03,098
What's wrong with that, right?

48
00:03:03,265 --> 00:03:04,778
Right.

49
00:03:05,106 --> 00:03:06,776
Bye, Ben.

50
00:04:37,897 --> 00:04:40,491
Oh, come on.

51
00:05:03,975 --> 00:05:05,249
Look out.

52
00:05:26,893 --> 00:05:30,124
All right, okay. Can I just ask you...

53
00:05:30,292 --> 00:05:32,045
...where am I now?

54
00:06:36,168 --> 00:06:41,684
Oh, man. Oh, God. Oh, God.
I'm okay. I'm okay.

55
00:06:42,207 --> 00:06:46,165
Accident. Woman in the middle
of the road with a cow!

56
00:06:46,846 --> 00:06:48,915
All right. I'm okay.

57
00:06:49,325 --> 00:06:52,796
Damn, my car.
