and plus housing.

249
00:19:39,063 --> 00:19:40,620
Twenty-seven thousand?

250
00:19:40,783 --> 00:19:44,251
- You see, Nick, I told you...
- Hold on. Thirty thousand.

251
00:19:45,141 --> 00:19:47,781
Look, you people don't even know me.

252
00:19:47,941 --> 00:19:50,500
I noticed right off that he
double-knots his shoelaces.

253
00:19:50,660 --> 00:19:53,175
- Excellent credentials.
- Shows he's careful.

254
00:19:53,582 --> 00:19:55,617
Anyway, don't you already have
a doctor?

255
00:19:55,781 --> 00:19:57,611
We got Hogue.
The problem with Hogue is...

256
00:19:57,780 --> 00:20:00,170
- He's old.
- Old and wholly unpleasant.

257
00:20:00,341 --> 00:20:02,410
Point is, he's not going
to be around forever.

258
00:20:02,619 --> 00:20:03,894
Thirty-five thousand?

259
00:20:04,060 --> 00:20:07,019
But that would take a unanimous vote
of the whole city council.

260
00:20:07,181 --> 00:20:09,135
- All in favor say, "Aye."
- Aye.

261
00:20:09,300 --> 00:20:11,575
- I abstain.
- You always abstain.

262
00:20:11,740 --> 00:20:15,573
Look, I appreciate your problem...

263
00:20:15,739 --> 00:20:17,695
...but I'm not the answer.

264
00:20:17,859 --> 00:20:20,135
I got a big job interview
on the West Coast.

265
00:20:20,299 --> 00:20:23,813
